data.description: Welcome Home to Wingfield! Nestled in the back side of a cul-de-sac, this exceptional residence is ready for you to make this your new home! A fantastic floor plan which accommodates a variety of lifestyles. Bright, open & cheery, your kitchen, sometimes referred to as the “Heart of the Home”, is great place for amazing meals and fulfilled conversations. Granite counters, center island, stainless steel appliances & loads of valuable counter & cabinet space.  Seller is offering a $1,500 paint allowance for kitchen cabinets. All bedrooms are restful, and the master suite is delightful & spacious - a great retreat to curl up with a book & really relax! This is a very comfortable residence located in a superb quiet neighborhood. A place and time for you to call home for many, enjoyable years to come. Come see today and start your new life tomorrow! Cheers!!
